{"tha-ap536:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap536:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap536:0.3":"Dabbamallaputtattheraapadana ","tha-ap536:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap536:1.2":"sabbalokavidu muni; ","tha-ap536:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap536:1.4":"kappe uppajji cakkhuma. ","tha-ap536:2.1":"Ovadako vinnapako, ","tha-ap536:2.2":"tarako sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap536:2.3":"Desanakusalo buddho, ","tha-ap536:2.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap536:3.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap536:3.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap536:3.3":"Sampatte titthiye sabbe, ","tha-ap536:3.4":"pancasile patitthapi. ","tha-ap536:4.1":"Evam nirakulam asi, ","tha-ap536:4.2":"sunnatam titthiyehi ca; ","tha-ap536:4.3":"Vicittam arahantehi, ","tha-ap536:4.4":"vasibhutehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap536:5.1":"Ratananatthapannasam, ","tha-ap536:5.2":"uggato so mahamuni; ","tha-ap536:5.3":"Kancanagghiyasankaso, ","tha-ap536:5.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","tha-ap536:6.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap536:6.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap536:6.3":"Tavata titthamano so, ","tha-ap536:6.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap536:7.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap536:7.2":"setthiputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap536:7.3":"Upetva lokapajjotam, ","tha-ap536:7.4":"assosim dhammadesanam. ","tha-ap536:8.1":"Senasanani bhikkhunam, ","tha-ap536:8.2":"pannapentam sasavakam; ","tha-ap536:8.3":"Kittayantassa vacanam, ","tha-ap536:8.4":"sunitva mudito aham. ","tha-ap536:9.1":"Adhikaram sasanghassa, ","tha-ap536:9.2":"katva tassa mahesino; ","tha-ap536:9.3":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","tha-ap536:9.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","tha-ap536:10.1":"Tadaha sa mahaviro, ","tha-ap536:10.2":"mama kammam pakittayam; ","tha-ap536:10.3":"‘Yo sasanghamabhojesi, ","tha-ap536:10.4":"sattaham lokanayakam. ","tha-ap536:11.1":"Soyam kamalapattakkho, ","tha-ap536:11.2":"sihamso kanakattaco; ","tha-ap536:11.3":"Mama padamule nipati, ","tha-ap536:11.4":"patthayam thanamuttamam. ","tha-ap536:12.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap536:12.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap536:12.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap536:12.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap536:13.1":"Savako tassa buddhassa, ","tha-ap536:13.2":"dabbo namena vissuto; ","tha-ap536:13.3":"Senasanapannapako, ","tha-ap536:13.4":"aggo hessatiyam tada’. ","tha-ap536:14.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap536:14.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap536:14.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap536:14.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap536:15.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap536:15.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap536:15.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap536:15.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap536:16.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap536:16.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap536:16.3":"Sabbattha sukhito asim, ","tha-ap536:16.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap536:17.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap536:17.2":"vipassi nama nayako; ","tha-ap536:17.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","tha-ap536:17.4":"sabbadhammavipassako. ","tha-ap536:18.1":"Dutthacitto upavadim, ","tha-ap536:18.2":"savakam tassa tadino; ","tha-ap536:18.3":"Sabbasavaparikkhinam, ","tha-ap536:18.4":"suddhoti ca vijaniya. ","tha-ap536:19.1":"Tasseva naravirassa, ","tha-ap536:19.2":"savakanam mahesinam; ","tha-ap536:19.3":"Salakanca gahetvana, ","tha-ap536:19.4":"khirodanamadasaham. ","tha-ap536:20.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap536:20.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","tha-ap536:20.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap536:20.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","tha-ap536:21.1":"Sasanam jotayitvana, ","tha-ap536:21.2":"abhibhuyya kutitthiye; ","tha-ap536:21.3":"Vineyye vinayitvava, ","tha-ap536:21.4":"nibbuto so sasavako. ","tha-ap536:22.1":"Sasisse nibbute nathe, ","tha-ap536:22.2":"atthamentamhi sasane; ","tha-ap536:22.3":"Deva kandimsu samvigga, ","tha-ap536:22.4":"muttakesa rudammukha. ","tha-ap536:23.1":"‘Nibbayissati dhammakkho, ","tha-ap536:23.2":"na passissama subbate; ","tha-ap536:23.3":"Na sunissama saddhammam, ","tha-ap536:23.4":"aho no appapunnata’. ","tha-ap536:24.1":"Tadayam pathavi sabba, ","tha-ap536:24.2":"acala sa calacala; ","tha-ap536:24.3":"Sagaro ca sasokova, ","tha-ap536:24.4":"vinadi karunam giram. ","tha-ap536:25.1":"Catuddisa dundubhiyo, ","tha-ap536:25.2":"nadayimsu amanusa; ","tha-ap536:25.3":"Samantato asaniyo, ","tha-ap536:25.4":"phalimsu ca bhayavaha. ","tha-ap536:26.1":"Ukka patimsu nabhasa, ","tha-ap536:26.2":"dhumaketu ca dissati; ","tha-ap536:26.3":"Sadhuma jalavatta ca, ","tha-ap536:26.4":"ravimsu karunam miga. ","tha-ap536:27.1":"Uppade darune disva, ","tha-ap536:27.2":"sasanatthangasucake; ","tha-ap536:27.3":"Samvigga bhikkhavo satta, ","tha-ap536:27.4":"cintayimha mayam tada. ","tha-ap536:28.1":"‘Sasanena vinamhakam, ","tha-ap536:28.2":"jivitena alam mayam; ","tha-ap536:28.3":"Pavisitva maharannam, ","tha-ap536:28.4":"yunjama jinasasanam’. ","tha-ap536:29.1":"Addasamha tadaranne, ","tha-ap536:29.2":"ubbiddham selamuttamam; ","tha-ap536:29.3":"Nisseniya tamaruyha, ","tha-ap536:29.4":"nissenim patayimhase. ","tha-ap536:30.1":"Tada ovadi no thero, ","tha-ap536:30.2":"‘buddhuppado sudullabho; ","tha-ap536:30.3":"Saddhatidullabha laddha, ","tha-ap536:30.4":"thokam sesanca sasanam. ","tha-ap536:31.1":"Nipatanti khanatita, ","tha-ap536:31.2":"anante dukkhasagare; ","tha-ap536:31.3":"Tasma payogo kattabbo, ","tha-ap536:31.4":"yava thati mune matam’. ","tha-ap536:32.1":"Araha asi so thero, ","tha-ap536:32.2":"anagami tadanugo; ","tha-ap536:32.3":"Susila itare yutta, ","tha-ap536:32.4":"devalokam agamhase. ","tha-ap536:33.1":"Nibbuto tinnasamsaro, ","tha-ap536:33.2":"suddhavase ca ekako; ","tha-ap536:33.3":"Ahanca pakkusati ca, ","tha-ap536:33.4":"sabhiyo bahiyo tatha. ","tha-ap536:34.1":"Kumarakassapo ceva, ","tha-ap536:34.2":"tattha tatthupaga mayam; ","tha-ap536:34.3":"Samsarabandhana mutta, ","tha-ap536:34.4":"gotamenanukampita. ","tha-ap536:35.1":"Mallesu kusinarayam, ","tha-ap536:35.2":"jato gabbheva me sato; ","tha-ap536:35.3":"Mata mata citarulha, ","tha-ap536:35.4":"tato nippatito aham. ","tha-ap536:36.1":"Patito dabbapunjamhi, ","tha-ap536:36.2":"tato dabboti vissuto; ","tha-ap536:36.3":"Brahmacaribalenaham, ","tha-ap536:36.4":"vimutto sattavassiko. ","tha-ap536:37.1":"Khirodanabalenaham, ","tha-ap536:37.2":"pancahangehupagato; ","tha-ap536:37.3":"Khinasavopavadena, ","tha-ap536:37.4":"papehi bahucodito. ","tha-ap536:38.1":"Ubho punnanca papanca, ","tha-ap536:38.2":"vitivattomhi daniham; ","tha-ap536:38.3":"Patvana paramam santim, ","tha-ap536:38.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap536:39.1":"Senasanam pannapayim, ","tha-ap536:39.2":"hasayitvana subbate; ","tha-ap536:39.3":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","tha-ap536:39.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap536:40.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap536:40.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap536:40.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap536:41.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap536:41.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap536:41.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap536:42.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap536:42.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap536:42.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap536:43.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dabbamallaputto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap536:44.1":"Dabbamallaputtattherassapadanam catuttham. "}